SELECT  feature, 
        max(avaSlo) as 'ava slo',
        ifnull(AVG(NULLIF(ava_debt ,0)),0) as 'ava debt',
        max(expSlo) as 'exp slo',
        ifnull(AVG(NULLIF(exp_debt ,0)),0) as 'exp debt',
        max(latSlo) as 'lat slo',
        ifnull(AVG(NULLIF(lat_debt ,0)),0) as 'lat debt'
FROM HourlyFeature
WHERE
$__timeFilter(start) 
Group by feature

SELECT
  ifnull(avg(nullif(ava_debt,0)),0)  as 'debt'
FROM HourlyFeature
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(start)   and feature = '$feature'

SELECT
  avg(exp_debt)  as 'debt'
FROM HourlyFeature
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(start) and exp_debt > 0  and feature = '$feature'

SELECT
  ifnull(avg(nullif(lat_debt,0)),0) as 'debt'
FROM HourlyFeature
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(start) and feature = '$feature'

SELECT
  source, 
  avg(ava_debt) as 'debt'
FROM HourlyFeature
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(start) and feature = '$feature'
group by source

SELECT
  source, 
  avg(exp_debt) as 'debt'
FROM HourlyFeature
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(start) and feature = '$feature'
group by source

SELECT
  source, 
  avg(lat_debt) as 'debt'
FROM HourlyFeature
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(start) and feature = '$feature'
group by source

SELECT  source, 
        max(avaSlo) as 'ava slo',
        ifnull(AVG(NULLIF(ava_debt ,0)),0) as 'ava debt',
        max(expSlo) as 'exp slo',
        ifnull(AVG(NULLIF(exp_debt ,0)),0) as 'exp debt',
        max(latSlo) as 'lat slo',
        ifnull(AVG(NULLIF(lat_debt ,0)),0) as 'lat debt'
FROM HourlyFeature
WHERE
$__timeFilter(start)  and feature='$feature'
Group by source

SELECT
  start AS "time",
  source,
  sum(total) as 'request'
FROM HourlyFeature
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(start) and feature = '$feature'
group by source, start
ORDER BY start

SELECT
  start AS "time",
  source,
  avg(lat) as 'latency ms'
FROM HourlyFeature
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(start) and feature = '$feature'
group by start, source
ORDER BY start
